<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>You're Invited!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #333;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Hi there,</p>
    <p>We're excited to invite you to join our team. Click the button below to accept the invitation:</p>
    <div class="button-container">
        <a href="<%= inviteLink %>" class="button">Join Now</a>
    </div>
    <p>Looking forward to having you with us!</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>Amit's Team</p>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="mailto:<%= supportMail %>">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
